trans-unit.source: Attribute that contains information about a Workflow markup file.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowMarkupSourceAttribute"></xref> class, initializing the values of <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowMarkupSourceAttribute.FileName*> and <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowMarkupSourceAttribute.MD5Digest*>.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.WorkflowMarkupSourceAttribute"></xref>类，初始化的值<> *1> 和<> *1>。
